Beginning with a senile monk who accidentally baptizes a flock of penguins, heaven is forced to grant them human souls and histories. Systematically recreating historical eras, from the Middle Ages to a hyper-capitalist future, the society evolves from primitive tribalism to an automated, self-destructive modern empire.

