Divided into two halves, the story explores a merchant's son seeking success on earth, and his post-mortal journey through various Heavens based on his spiritual karma. Utilizing traditional Buddhist parables and encounters with Gautama Buddha, the protagonist slowly sheds worldly attachments to reach absolute enlightenment.

