A dual narrative engine tracks the transformation of a cynical Roman patrician through love and the systemic persecution of a religious minority. Meticulously detailed architecture, social hierarchies, and brutal spectacles of ancient Rome frame a psychological conversion that mirrors the cultural shifts threatening the empire.

